air:Brand.Name: ECO STANDARD

ECOSTAND
air:Brand.air:Text: Upgrade to Economy Standard to check in a bag.

Enjoy comfortable seating in Lufthansa long-haul Economy Class, coupled with great fares.
· 1 piece checked luggage up to 23 kg · 1 carry-on bag · Complimentary snacks and drinks to suit the flight time · Extensive programme of in flight entertainment · Lufthansa FlyNet® WiFi for a small fee · Collect miles for every flight
